		</li>
		<li class="ibox-similarto clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><ul class="smw-format ul-format"><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Expressing_&quot;never_again&quot;_with_&quot;zai_ye_bu&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;never again&quot; with &quot;zai ye bu&quot;">Expressing "never again" with "zai ye bu"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">B2</span></span>)</li></ul></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-similarto-hsk clearfix" style="display:none;">
			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><ul class="smw-format ul-format"><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Expressing_&quot;never_again&quot;_with_&quot;zai_ye_bu&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;never again&quot; with &quot;zai ye bu&quot;">Expressing "never again" with "zai ye bu"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK5</span></span>)</li></ul></div>
